What effect does currency decreasing in value have? -- It will be cheaper to buy that country's products in other countries. --
What effect does currency increasing in value have? -- It will be more expensive to buy that country's products in other countries. --
What effect does a low interest rate have? -- More money for borrowing, more spending. Thus economy and demand for goods grows and inflation increases. --
What effect does a high interest rate have? -- Less money and more saving. Thus economy slows, demand is less than supply and inflation decreases. --
